emic research and faculty positions at postsecondary institutions to commercial enterprise startup growth and management additionally experienced in law enforcement forensics and technology innovation for the united states department of defense and department of homeland security primary solutions innovated include the development and application of nonrf covert communications unique capability physical security sensors as well as intelligent system solutions for the detection and assessment of events of interest erin phelps vice president global sales based in the washington dc area erin will be responsible for leading bds sales activities mr phelps’s career in the security industry and system integration market has spanned over  years during his tenure he has held senior positions in sales marketing business development and program management prior to joining bds mr phelps held key executive positions as sr vice president at the mariner group as well as vice president of enterprise security solutions at ciber federal division mr phelps has worked to provide security solutions in key vertical markets including homeland security public safety commercial building security utilitiesenergy event security and other critical infrastructure security markets newsletter downloads ronin datasheet latest news press release – bds receives contract for global data center security deployment of ronin ronin has taken flight storming beaches and finding mines with the us navy ronin is lab tested by ncs a leading academic institution in the united states in sport safety and security   schedule a free demo of ronin notice javascript is required for this content ronin – broadband discovery systems worlds first intelligent threat detection platform deployed by the military now commercially ready with unmatched throughput rate specific signature detection and covert deployments that integrate with legacy systems   threat analytics proprietary sensors and signal processing algorithms cr